# Media: track ONLY the demo fixture; exclude everything else.
# App/public/videos/ and the non-fixture App/public/data/ dirs were the leak
# vector (previously uncovered), so `git add -A` would have staged
# copyright-derived renders. Deny-all, then re-allow the single fixture that
# seeds the README hero and the zero-key demo.
# NOTE: re-bake the ce907eaa clip from a CC-BY / public-domain source before push.
App/public/videos/*
!App/public/videos/ce907eaa-6229-4d18-bff0-ff8c54bac048.mp4
App/public/data/*/
!App/public/data/ce907eaa-6229-4d18-bff0-ff8c54bac048/
App/public/vibe.mp4

